          <h2 class="h5 fw-bold">Bells Fork Auto &amp; Truck</h2>
          <p class="small-muted">
            Auto repair and truck service in Greenville, NC—diagnostics, maintenance, and repairs you can trust.
          </p>
          <p class="mb-1"><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href="tel:+12524960005">(252) 496-0005</a></p>
          <p class="mb-1"><strong>Address:</strong> 3840 Charles Blvd, Greenville, NC 27858</p>
          <p class="mb-0"><strong>Hours:</strong> Mon–Fri 8:00 AM–5:30 PM</p>
        </div>

        <div class="col-lg-4">
          <h2 class="h6 fw-bold">Quick Links</h2>
          <ul class="list-unstyled">
            <li><a class="text-decoration-none" href="#services">Services</a></li>
            <li><a class="text-decoration-none" href="#about">About</a></li>
            <li><a class="text-decoration-none" href="#reviews">Reviews</a></li>
            <li><a class="text-decoration-none" href="#service-area">Service Area</a></li>
