            <li>Keep your Name/Address/Phone identical everywhere (site, Google Business Profile, directories).</li>
            <li>Add real service photos with descriptive file names + alt text (fast-loading WebP).</li>
            <li>Replace sample testimonials with verified customer reviews.</li>
            <li>Create location/service pages later (e.g., /brake-repair-greenville-nc/) for stronger rankings.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <hr class="border-light border-opacity-25 my-4">

      <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row justify-content-between gap-2 small">
        <div>© <span id="year"></span> Bells Fork Auto &amp; Truck. All rights reserved.</div>
        <div class="d-flex gap-3">
          <a class="text-decoration-none" href="/privacy">Privacy</a>
          <a class="text-decoration-none" href="/terms">Terms</a>
        </div>
